### Get All Newsletters
GET http://localhost:5000/api/newsletters
Accept: application/json

###

### Get All Newsletters with Pagination
GET http://localhost:5000/api/newsletters?page=1&limit=10&orderBy=createdAt&order=desc
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Latest Newsletters
GET http://localhost:5000/api/newsletters/latest?limit=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Newsletter by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/newsletters/NEWSLETTER_ID_HERE
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Newsletter (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/newsletters
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="headline"

New Food Distribution Program Announced
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

We are excited to announce a new food distribution program starting next month. This program will serve over 500 families in the community and provide weekly food packages including fresh produce, grains, and protein sources.
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="adminId"

YOUR_ADMIN_ID_HERE
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### Update Newsletter (Admin Only)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/newsletters/NEWSLETTER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="headline"

Updated: New Food Distribution Program
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

UPDATED: We are excited to announce a new food distribution program starting next month. Registration is now open!
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### Delete Newsletter (Admin Only)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/newsletters/NEWSLETTER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

